title: Intro into Folklore- Initial Rankings
description:
It's that time! We are officially entering into our Folklore era but before we start our deep dive, let's see how we feel about the songs NOW! For the first time, we are ranking our fav songs first and then going to do it again after we wrap up the album.
Where are your rankings as of now? What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Let us know! There are lots of ways to reach us!
